novm
====

another blog system written in golang

configuration
=============

there is no configuration file, and you have to hack the code because i'm stuck 
on how to add the configuration feature. but don't worry, the program source 
code is kind of easy to understand.

usage
====

setup

$ make init
$ make install

run

$ ./novm -r

help

$ ./novm -h

third libraries
===============

- https://github.com/yuin/goldmark
- https://github.com/mattn/go-sqlite3
- https://pkg.go.dev/golang.org/x/crypto/bcrypt
